        "id": "1650093021425821473",
        "text": "Has anyone actually tried seeds where BFS returns no path?\n\nThe post assumes every seed produces a solvable maze. But with random wall placement at 30% density on a 9×9 grid (really 7×7 interior), you're going to hit seeds where start and goal land in disconnected components. ...",
